<chapter line="1">19. Kuṭajapupphiyavaggo</chapter>
<subhead line="2">1-10. Kuṭajapupphiyattheraapadānādivaṇṇanā</subhead>
<paragraph line="3">Ito <pageBreak edition="P" number="0.0465" /><pageBreak edition="V" number="2.0175" /> parampi ekūnavīsatimavagge āgatānaṃ imesaṃ kuṭajapupphiyattherādīnaṃ dasannaṃ therānaṃ apubbaṃ natthi. Tesañhi therānaṃ purimabuddhānaṃ santike katapuññasambhārānaṃ vasena pākaṭanāmāni ceva nivāsanagarādīni ca heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva veditabbānīti taṃ sabbaṃ apadānaṃ suviññeyyamevāti.</paragraph>
<centered line="4">Ekūnavīsatimavaggavaṇṇanā samattā.</centered>
